Package itb.arkavquarium

Interface Aquatic

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Coin, Guppy, Pellet, Piranha, Snail

    interface Aquatic

    Aquatic! The Aquatic interface defines all objects in Aquarium. This contains all the needed information of the object in the Aquarium to be drawn.

    Since:
    2018-04-15
    Version:
    0.0
    Author:
    Abram Situmorang, Faza Fahleraz, Senapati Sang Diwangkara, Yusuf Rahmat Pratama
